s, cell culture media, and serum, as well as general labware, and glassware and equipment under the Corning, Pyrex, Falcon, and Axygen brands. The company was formerly known as Corning Glass Works and changed its name to Corning Incorporated in April 1989. Corning Incorporated was founded in 1851 and is headquartered in Corning, New York.", "fullTimeEmployees": 56300, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Wendell P. Weeks", "age": 64, "title": "Chairman & CEO", "yearBorn": 1960, "fiscalYear": 2024, "totalPay": 12492989, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 9059841}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Lewis A. Steverson J.D.", "age": 60, "title": "Vice Chairman, EVP & Chief Legal and Administrative Officer", "yearBorn": 1964, "fiscalYear": 2024, "totalPay": 4286842, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Eric S. Musser", "age": 64, "title": "President & COO", "yearBorn": 1960, "fiscalYear": 2024, "totalPay": 5781535, "exercisedValue": 509010, "unexercisedValue": 525350}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Edward A. Schlesinger", "age": 56, "title": "Executive Vice President & Chief Financial Officer", "yearBorn": 1968, "fiscalYear": 2024, "totalPay": 2920317, "exercisedValue": 503772, "unexercisedValue": 369018}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Avery H. Nelson III", "age": 55, "title": "EVP & GM of Automotive, Live Sciences & Solar", "yearBorn": 1969, "fiscalYear": 2024, "totalPay": 2477373, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 841832}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. John Z. Zhang", "age": 51, "title": "EVP & Chief Corporate Development Officer", "yearBorn": 1973, "fiscalYear": 2024, "totalPay": 4311457, "exercisedValue": 148575, "unexercisedValue": 170394}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Dr. Jaymin  Amin", "age": 55, "title": "Senior VP & CTO", "yearBorn": 1969, "fiscalYear": 2024, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Soumya  Seetharam", "age": 48, "title": "Senior VP and Chief Digital & Information Officer", "year